Package lawnlayer

Class Shield

  • java.lang.Object
    • lawnlayer.GameObject
      • lawnlayer.Shield
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PowerUp
    public class Shield
extends GameObject
implements PowerUp
    A singleton subclass of GameObject and implementation of PowerUp. This power up turns the Player invincible for a brief period of time. All Enemy types will bounce off the Player and path will not turn red upon collision.
